    "description": "30-case evaluation suite for L2 chronic-disease-observer skill. This skill receives weekly aggregation data with alert_class lifestyle_regularity, calls search_hpa_guidelines (category: chronic_disease_lifestyle, exclude_medical: true), and outputs structured JSON for weekly-summary-composer. It does NOT call generate_line_report.",
